    "description": "Metropolis - The Ultimate City Simulator<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMetropolis is a city simulator like no other. In your role as Mayor you need to rebuild and regenerate your city to become one of the best in the world. Financial mismanagement has brought the city to it's knees and the previous administration are facing many accusations of corruption and embezzlement.<br />\r\n <br />\r\nAs the newly elected Mayor your challenge is to rebuild the city to become the top 'most liveable city' in the world. Your task won't be easy, all essential services have been run down and the major buildings of the city have fallen into disrepair. While breathing life back into the city you'll have to watch your back, political opponents are ready to strike at every opportunity and your fate will be decided by the voters at the next election.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nKey Features...<br />\r\n​Over 60 building types<br />\r\nDay and night cycles<br />\r\nOpposition parties and elections<br />\r\nPress conferences<br />\r\nComprehensive policy options<br />\r\n4 types of public transport<br />\r\nFully functioning stock exchange<br />\r\nDetailed financial information<br />\r\n5 types of tax income<br />\r\nFully functional global economy<br />\r\nIntelligent news channel<br />\r\nChanging land and property values<br />\r\nBuild, invest and sell property<br />\r\nDetailed crime statistics<br />\r\nCCTV and Police Helicopter<br />\r\nDistinct and unique city suburbs",
